        <article  id="cast" class="">
    
    <section id="better-together-google-cast-desktop-us"
      class="android-hero-full-bleed android-spacer-margin-top--3 hidden--xs hidden--sm hidden--md hidden--lg nimble-priority-component android-hero-full-bleed--full-bleed android-hero-full-bleed--vertical-reversed android-hero-full-bleed--small-container android-hero-full-bleed--black android-hero-full-bleed--left"
       data-module="hero" data-section-header="Put your small screen on your big screen."
      data-nimble-component="DsHeroFullBleed"
      data-nimble-component-config="{&#39;blockClass&#39;: &#39;android-hero-full-bleed&#39;, &#39;hasAnimation&#39;: False}">
    <div class="android-hero-full-bleed__wrapper android-grid"><div class="android-hero-full-bleed__copy-wrapper"><div class="android-badge android-hero-full-bleed__badge  android-background android-background--semantic-5" aria-hidden="true" style=""><span class="android-badge__label">Google Cast</span>
  </div><h1 class="android-hero-full-bleed__heading android-heading android-heading--h2">Tonton konten dari layar kecil perangkat Anda di layar TV.</h1><p class="android-hero-full-bleed__copy android-body android-body--large">Transmisikan film, musik, acara TV, dan lainnya dari ponsel ke TV Anda dengan Google Cast. Dengan lebih dari 3.000 aplikasi yang kompatibel untuk Google Cast – termasuk Netflix, Spotify, TikTok – Anda bisa menikmati hiburan tanpa gangguan.<sup>3</sup></p><button class="android-cta android-hero-full-bleed__cta  android-cta--md  android-cta--primary" aria-label="Lihat cara kerjanya" data-ga-config="{&#34;click&#34;: {&#34;event&#34;: &#34;trackEvent&#34;, &#34;eventCategory&#34;: &#34;module interactions&#34;, &#34;eventAction&#34;: &#34;cta click&#34;, &#34;moduleName&#34;: &#34;Put your small screen on your big screen.&#34;, &#34;linkUrl&#34;: &#34;&#34;, &#34;eventLabel&#34;: &#34;See how it works&#34;}}" data-nimble-component="DsModalOpener" data-modal="beto-google-cast">
    <span>Lihat cara kerjanya      <svg
      aria-hidden="true"
    class="android-cta__icon"
    >
    <use href="#add-icon"></use>
  </svg>

</span></button></div>
    </div>  <div class="background background--primary-1"><div id="beto-google-cast" class="android-video background__video "
