</section><section id="beto-google-cast-mobile-us"
       data-module="content multimedia" data-section-header="Put your small screen on your big screen."
      class="android-content-multimedia android-spacer-margin-top--3 hidden--xl hidden--xxl android-content-multimedia--reversed android-content-multimedia--full-bleed android-content-multimedia--has-space-between android-content-multimedia--video-full-bleed">
    <div class="android-content-multimedia__wrapper android-grid">
      <div class="android-content-multimedia__copy-wrapper"><div class="android-badge android-content-multimedia__badge  android-background android-background--semantic-5" aria-hidden="true" style=""><span class="android-badge__label">Google Cast</span>
  </div><h1 class="android-content-multimedia__heading android-heading android-heading--h2">Menonton konten dari perangkat layar kecil ke layar TV.</h1><p class="android-content-multimedia__copy android-body android-body--large">Transmisikan film, musik, acara TV, dan lainnya dari ponsel ke TV dengan Google Cast. Dengan lebih dari 3.000+ aplikasi yang kompatibel untuk Google Cast – termasuk Netflix, Spotify, TikTok – Anda bisa menikmati hiburan tanpa gangguan.<sup>3</sup></p><button class="android-cta android-content-multimedia__cta  android-cta--md  android-cta--primary" aria-label="Lihat cara kerjanya" data-ga-config="{&#34;click&#34;: {&#34;event&#34;: &#34;trackEvent&#34;, &#34;eventCategory&#34;: &#34;module interactions&#34;, &#34;eventAction&#34;: &#34;cta click&#34;, &#34;moduleName&#34;: &#34;Put your small screen on your big screen.&#34;, &#34;linkUrl&#34;: &#34;&#34;, &#34;eventLabel&#34;: &#34;See how it works&#34;}}" data-nimble-component="DsModalOpener" data-modal="beto-google-cast">
    <span>Lihat cara kerjanya      <svg
      aria-hidden="true"
    class="android-cta__icon"
    >
    <use href="#add-icon"></use>
  </svg>

</span></button></div>
