</section><section id="beto-quick-share-modal-share-with-qr-code-desktop"  data-module="blocks" class="android-blocks-default hidden--xs hidden--sm hidden--md hidden--lg  android-blocks-default--full-bleed  android-blocks-default--has-eyebrow" >
    <div class="android-blocks-default__wrapper android-grid"><p class="android-blocks-default__eyebrow android-eyebrow android-eyebrow--default">Bagikan menggunakan kode QR</p><div class="android-blocks-default__content"><h4 class="android-blocks-default__heading-primary android-heading android-heading--h3">Pindai kode QR dan bagikan file dalam sekejap.</h4><p class="android-blocks-default__heading-secondary android-body android-body--large">Berbagi konten dengan perangkat di sekitar menjadi cepat dan mudah. Cukup pilih konten, buat kode QR, lalu minta penerima memindai kode di layar Anda. Selesai!
<br>
<br>
<span class="is-footnote">*Tersedia di perangkat seluler dan tablet. Perangkat harus berada dalam jangkauan efektif Bluetooth dan telah mengaktifkan Wi-Fi.</span></p><a class="android-cta  android-cta--md  android-cta--tertiary" href="https://support.google.com/android/answer/9286773?hl=en#zippy=%2Cshare-content-with-someone:~:text=Share%20%26%20receive%20content%20on%20your%20Android%20device" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Pelajari caranya (Membuka di tab baru)" data-ga-config="{&#34;click&#34;: {&#34;event&#34;: &#34;trackEvent&#34;, &#34;eventCategory&#34;: &#34;module interactions&#34;, &#34;eventAction&#34;: &#34;cta click&#34;, &#34;moduleName&#34;: &#34;Scan a QR code, and share files in a snap.&#34;, &#34;linkUrl&#34;: &#34;https://support.google.com/android/answer/9286773?hl=en#zippy=%2Cshare-content-with-someone:~:text=Share%20%26%20receive%20content%20on%20your%20Android%20device&#34;, &#34;eventLabel&#34;: &#34;Learn how&#34;}}">
    <span>Pelajari caranya      <svg
      aria-hidden="true"
    class="android-cta__icon"
    >
    <use href="#arrow-external"></use>
  </svg>

</span>
  </a></div>
