       data-module="content multimedia" data-section-header="Scan a QR code, and share files in a snap."
      class="android-content-multimedia android-spacer-padding-top--4 android-spacer-padding-bottom--4 hidden--xl hidden--xxl">
    <div class="android-content-multimedia__wrapper android-grid">
      <div class="android-content-multimedia__copy-wrapper"><p class="android-content-multimedia__eyebrow android-eyebrow android-eyebrow--default">Berbagi dengan Kode QR</p><h3 class="android-content-multimedia__heading android-heading android-heading--h4">Pindai kode QR dan bagikan file dalam sekejap.</h3><p class="android-content-multimedia__copy android-body android-body--large">Berbagi konten dengan perangkat di sekitar menjadi cepat dan mudah. Cukup pilih konten, buat kode QR, lalu minta penerima memindai kode di layar Anda. Selesai!
<br>
<br>
<span class="is-footnote">*Tersedia di perangkat seluler dan tablet. Perangkat harus berada dalam jangkauan efektif Bluetooth dan telah mengaktifkan Wi-Fi.</span></p><a class="android-cta android-content-multimedia__cta  android-cta--md  android-cta--tertiary" href="https://support.google.com/android/answer/9286773?hl=en#zippy=%2Cshare-content-with-someone:~:text=Share%20%26%20receive%20content%20on%20your%20Android%20device" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Pelajari caranya (Membuka di tab baru)" data-ga-config="{&#34;click&#34;: {&#34;event&#34;: &#34;trackEvent&#34;, &#34;eventCategory&#34;: &#34;module interactions&#34;, &#34;eventAction&#34;: &#34;cta click&#34;, &#34;moduleName&#34;: &#34;Scan a QR code, and share files in a snap.&#34;, &#34;linkUrl&#34;: &#34;https://support.google.com/android/answer/9286773?hl=en#zippy=%2Cshare-content-with-someone:~:text=Share%20%26%20receive%20content%20on%20your%20Android%20device&#34;, &#34;eventLabel&#34;: &#34;Learn how&#34;}}">
