    <div class="android-blocks-default__wrapper android-grid"><p class="android-blocks-default__eyebrow android-eyebrow android-eyebrow--default">Berbagi dengan PC Windows</p><div class="android-blocks-default__content"><h4 class="android-blocks-default__heading-primary android-heading android-heading--h3">Bekerja lebih cerdas, bukan lebih keras.</h4><p class="android-blocks-default__heading-secondary android-body android-body--large">Tidak perlu lagi mengirim email ke diri sendiri atau menggunakan Cloud. Quick Share memungkinkan Anda mentransfer foto, video, dokumen, atau folder antar-perangkat Windows dan Android dengan mudah. Perlu mengedit saat sedang dalam perjalanan? Bagikan file ke ponsel.
<br>
<br>
Untuk memulai, <a style="color: var(--primary);" href="/better-together/quick-share-app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-ga-config="{&quot;click&quot;: {&quot;event&quot;: &quot;trackEvent&quot;, &quot;eventCategory&quot;: &quot;module interactions&quot;, &quot;eventAction&quot;: &quot;conversion cta click&quot;, &quot;moduleName&quot;: &quot;Work smarter, not harder.&quot;, &quot;linkUrl&quot;: &quot;/better-together/quick-share-app/&quot;, &quot;eventLabel&quot;: &quot;download&quot;}}"><b>download</b></a> dan instal Quick Share ke perangkat Windows.</p><a class="android-cta  android-cta--md  android-cta--tertiary" href="/intl/id_id/better-together/quick-share-app/" aria-label="Pelajari lebih lanjut" data-ga-config="{&#34;click&#34;: {&#34;event&#34;: &#34;trackEvent&#34;, &#34;eventCategory&#34;: &#34;module interactions&#34;, &#34;eventAction&#34;: &#34;cta click&#34;, &#34;moduleName&#34;: &#34;Work smarter, not harder.&#34;, &#34;linkUrl&#34;: &#34;/intl/id_id/better-together/quick-share-app/&#34;, &#34;eventLabel&#34;: &#34;Learn more&#34;}}">
