      <div class="android-modal-components-default__inner-container"><section id="beto-updates-modal-wear-os"  data-module="blocks" class="android-blocks-default  android-blocks-default--vertically-reverse  android-blocks-default--full-bleed" >
    <div class="android-blocks-default__wrapper android-grid"><div class="android-blocks-default__content"><div class="android-badge  android-background android-background--semantic-light-5" aria-hidden="true" style=""><span class="android-badge__label">Wear OS</span>
  </div><h4 class="android-blocks-default__heading-primary android-heading android-heading--h3">Membuat selfie menarik dari pergelangan tangan Anda.</h4><p class="android-blocks-default__heading-secondary android-body android-body--large">Ingin membuat selfie tampak lebih menarik? Anda kini bisa mengambil foto tanpa perlu memegang ponsel. Jauhkan diri dari kamera, berpose, dan ambil foto terbaik hanya dengan satu ketukan di pergelangan tangan.
<br>
<br>
<span class="is-footnote">Smartwatch dijual terpisah. Aplikasi bisa didownload di smartwatch Wear OS versi apa pun (Wear OS 3 dan yang lebih baru). Hanya berfungsi dengan ponsel Pixel.</span></p><a class="android-cta  android-cta--md  android-cta--primary" href="https://support.google.com/wearos/answer/11532572#:~:text=When%20you%20download%20the%20Google,OS%20Wear%202%20and%20above." target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Pelajari lebih lanjut (Membuka di tab baru)" data-ga-config="{&#34;click&#34;: {&#34;event&#34;: &#34;trackEvent&#34;, &#34;eventCategory&#34;: &#34;module interactions&#34;, &#34;eventAction&#34;: &#34;cta click&#34;, &#34;moduleName&#34;: &#34;Up your selfie game from your wrist.&#34;, &#34;linkUrl&#34;: &#34;https://support.google.com/wearos/answer/11532572#:~:text=When%20you%20download%20the%20Google,OS%20Wear%202%20and%20above.&#34;, &#34;eventLabel&#34;: &#34;Learn more&#34;}}">
    <span>Pelajari lebih lanjut      <svg
      aria-hidden="true"
    class="android-cta__icon"
    >
    <use href="#arrow-external"></use>
  </svg>

